《归来之翼》到2008年8月8日时全球售出104万，其中日本54万、北美22万、欧洲28万<ref>{{cite web | date=2008-08-08 | title=Annual Report 2008 | url=http://www.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/ar/20080808_01.pdf#page=11 | work=Square-Enix.com | accessdate=2008-12-20 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206115259/http://www.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/ar/20080808_01.pdf#page=11 | archivedate=2008年12月6日 }} </ref>。游戏发售周登上日本周畅销主机游戏首位，次周位列第二<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.the-magicbox.com/topten.htm | title=Top 30 Japanese Console Game Chart | accessdate=2007-07-06 | year=2007 | work=[http://www.the-magicbox.com/ The Magic Box] | archive-date=2007-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070705013646/http://www.the-magicbox.com/topten.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

日本版获《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》32/40的评价<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/final-fantasy-xii-revenant-wings-first-impressions?page=2 | title=First Impressions - Final Fantasy XII: Revenant Wings | accessdate=2007-07-06 | author=Parkin, Simon | date=2007-05-28 | work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | publisher=Eurogamer Network | pages=2 | archive-date=2009-08-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804023721/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/final-fantasy-xii-revenant-wings-first-impressions?page=2 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[电击任天堂|电击DS & Wii风格]]》称赞游戏的任务式情节，战斗“简单并有更多的参与”。游戏支持大量角色同时参战，带给玩家“亲临作战”之感，游戏难度几可吸引“不常玩角色扮演游戏”的感觉。游戏触控笔划选战区不畅招致批评<ref>{{cite web | url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/780/780805p1.html | title=FFXII: Revenant Wings Reviewed | accessdate=2007-04-16 | author=Gantayat, Anoop | date=2007-04-16 | work=[[IGN|IGN]] | publisher=[[News_Corporation|News Corporation]] | archive-date=2007-04-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070421112142/http://ds.ign.com/articles/780/780805p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

北美版游戏主获积极评分，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的汇总得分为81/100。《[[电子游戏月刊|电子游戏月刊]]》三名评测者分别打出8、7.5和6分（满分皆为10分），评论赞扬游戏角色扮演与策略的结合，但批评画面尺寸难称大量行动单位<ref>Electronic Gaming Monthly, Issue 223; HOL. 2007</ref>。本作是IGN 2007年11月的月度任天堂DS游戏<ref>{{cite web | url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/838/838955p1.html | title=Nintendo DS Game of the Month: November 2007 | accessdate=2007-12-01 | author=Harris, Craig | date=2007-11-30 | work=[[IGN|IGN]] | publisher=[[News_Corporation|News Corporation]] | archive-date=2007-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071201213554/http://ds.ign.com/articles/838/838955p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
